Subject: [PATCH 3/4] backport nv_timeval changes from 440.82

---
 common/inc/nv-time.h                  | 10 ++++-
 conftest.sh                           | 62 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 nvidia-modeset/nvidia-modeset-linux.c |  2 +-
 nvidia-modeset/nvidia-modeset.Kbuild  |  1 +
